arm_group.description:
(IV dose at 0.3 mg/kg, 1.0 mg/kg, 2.5 mg/kg, or 5.0 mg/kg)
Subjects:
SAD cohort - single IV dose;
MAD cohort - multiple (three) IV doses every two weeks;
Adaptive MAD cohort - multiple (five) IV doses up to the maximum tolerated MAD dose every week

